org.openbel.framework.core.kam
Class JdbcKAMLoaderImpl

java.lang.Object
  org.openbel.framework.core.df.AbstractJdbcDAO
      org.openbel.framework.core.kam.JdbcKAMLoaderImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
KAMLoader
public class JdbcKAMLoaderImpl
extends AbstractJdbcDAO
implements KAMLoader

JdbcKAMLoaderImpl implements a KAMLoader to load a KAM into the KAMstore schema using Jdbc.

The PreparedStatement resources are managed in AbstractJdbcDAO so one must take care in calling AbstractJdbcDAO.terminate() after the KAMLoader DAO is used.

Author:
Anthony Bargnesi <abargnesi@selventa.com>
